Sustrans
winning a nationwide vote in 2007
to create new walking and cycling routes
across the UK funded by 
the Big Lottery Fund
Amy Williams
English skeleton racer and Olympic gold medalist
Harry Patch 1898-2009
Born in Bath, he was the last surviving soldier to have fought in the trenches of the First World War
Roman Centurion
The Romans built their great Baths and Temple at the Sacred Spring in Bath"Č
